Package org.kuali.kfs.gl.businessobject.options

Class Summary
ActualBalanceTypeOptionFinder A value finder that returns all balance type, but selects the actual balance type
AmountViewOptionFinder An implementation of ValuesFinder that allows GL inquiries to select either monthly totals or accumulated totals on balance inquiries
BlankLineOptionFinder An implmentation of ValueFinder that allows the balance inquiries to choose whether to show blank entries
ConsolidationOptionFinder An implementation of ValueFinder that allows balance inquiries to choose between consolidated results or detailed results
CorrectionChooseSystemValuesFinder This class returns list, ready for populating a drop down select control, of "systems" that can be used by the GLCP
CorrectionEditMethodValuesFinder This class returns list of GLCP editing methods key value pairs, to populate a dropdown select control
CorrectionGroupEntriesFinder Returns list of GL origin entry filenames
CostShareOptionFinder An implmentation of ValueFinder that allows the balance inquiries to choose whether to include or exclude cost share entries
EncumbranceBalanceTypeOptionFinder An implementation of ValueFinder that returns all balance types, but which defaults to external encumbrance
OEGDateComparator A comparator for two origin entry groups, based on the dates of their creations
OEGIdComparator A comparator for origin entry groups, based on their group IDs
OriginEntryFieldFinder An extension of KeyValuesBase that
PendingEntryOptionFinder An implementation of ValueFinder that allows inquirers to include no pending entries, approved pending entries, or all pending entries in the results of their lookup
PeriodCodeOptionFinder An implementation of ValueFinder that allows the selection of a period code
ProcessingCorrectionGroupEntriesFinder Returns a list of done files in batch origin entry directory
SearchOperatorsFinder An extension of KeyValueBase that gives the user a choice of search operator options
